A wasu lokatai, hakan yakan sa yanayin ya yi sanyi sosai a nesa.
Wani misali na bambancin yanayin zafi tsakanin tsakiyar Amurka an lura da shi a ranar Lahadi.
Akwai bambanci kusan digiri 10 tsakanin Kansas City, Missouri da Omaha, Nebraska da tsakanin St. Louis da Des Moines, Iowa.
