Sama da masu kallo miliyan 20 sun kalli shaidar mai neman babban kotun Amurka Brett Kavanaugh a ranar Alhamis da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da laifin lalata da aka yi a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blaise Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, matsalar siyasa ta ci gaba, tare da cibiyoyin watsa labarai suna katse shirin na yau da kullun don juyawa a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi game da binciken mako guda na FBI game da zargin.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa ta tabbata da gaske cewa a wani biki da suka yi a makarantar sakandare, Kavanaugh ya yi mata hari yayin da yake bugu kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinta.
Kavanaugh ya bayyana cewa ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Bisa ga ma'aunin Nielsen, ana iya samun masu kallo fiye da miliyan 20.4 a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya lissafta matsakaicin kallon talabijin a kan cibiyoyin sadarwa na CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a ba da lambobin nan da nan ga sauran cibiyoyin da suka watsa wannan sauraron ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
A wani ɓangare kuma, Nielsen yana da wuya a ƙididdige yawan masu kallo da ke kallon watsa shirye-shirye daga ofisoshin.
