Kafar yada labarai ta Fox News, wacce 'yan jaridarta suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ta samu matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a yayin sauraron ranar, a cewar Nielsen.
A matsayi na biyu, akwai ABC da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta biyo baya da miliyan 3.1, NBC da miliyan 2.94, MSNBC da miliyan 2.89 da CNN da miliyan 2.52, a cewar Nielsen.
