Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron jama'a da ke birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump ya shirya yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da rangadin yankuna masu makwabtaka da juna kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake zabarsa a Kotun Koli na Amurka yana jiran a tabbatar da shi, Trump yana neman karfafa goyon bayan jama'a a zaben da ke tafe, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana a yau da dare kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon sa ta yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na yamma ET daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Ana iya ganin Trump ya yi magana ne game da sauraron karar da aka yi a wannan makon game da takarar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya faru a cikin yanayi mai tsauri saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i, tare da kuri'ar tabbatar da Majalisar Dattawa da aka dakatar har zuwa mako guda yayin da binciken FBI ke gudana.
Amma babban burin taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar rashin nasara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba don samun karfin gwiwa.
A cewar ofishin yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump, wadannan tarurruka biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, na nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka shugaban yana tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya yayin da muke tafiya a lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
Taron da aka shirya a daren yau a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling zai iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma su jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Republican a West Virginia, wanda ke cikin ƙananan ƙididdiga.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo ya yi kokarin ba shi damar zuwa kuri'un zabe", in ji Simon Hender, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
Ryder Cup 2018: Tawagar Amurka ta samu karfin gwiwa ta ci gaba da fafatawa yayin da take kan hanyar zuwa wasan daya a ranar Lahadi
Bayan wasa uku na wasa guda, wasannin hudu na ranar Asabar da yamma na iya zama abin da wannan gasar Ryder ta buƙaci.
Rashin karfin gwiwa shine tunanin wasanni, amma 'yan wasan suna gaskanta da shi, musamman a irin wannan wasanni.
A ina ne za su ce yanzu ne ake samun ci gaba?
"Sai dai sun yi gaba da digiri shida kuma yanzu suna gaba da hudu, saboda haka muna da ɗan gajeren lokaci", in ji Jordan Spith yayin da yake barin rana.
Turai tana da fa'ida, a bayyane take, ta ci gaba da maki hudu, kuma akwai maki 12 a wasan.
Amurkawa, kamar yadda Spith ya ce, suna jin "iska a cikin jirgin ruwa" kuma suna da abubuwa da yawa don ƙarfafa su, kamar su Spith da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu ya sami maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Spithe ya kashe mutane daga tee zuwa green kuma yana kafa misali.
Muryoyin murna sun kara daɗa ƙarfi yayin da ya ci gaba da zagaye, yana yin wani abu mai mahimmanci don ɗaukar wasan hudu-duka-duka lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance biyu bayan biyu.
An yi bikin lashe wasan a ranar 15 ga watan Agusta, wanda ya nuna cewa ya tabbata cewa tawagar Amurka ba ta fita ba.
"Dole ne ka duba cikinka sosai kuma ka damu da wasan da kake yi", in ji Spith.
Wannan shi ne abin da kowane dan wasa ya bari.
Ramin 18 don yin tarihi.
'Yan wasa kawai da suka fi Spithe da Thomas maki a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, tarihin gasar Ryder.
Ƙwararrun 'yan'uwa biyu na Turai sun yi nasara a kan hudu daga cikin hudu kuma ba su yi wani abu ba daidai ba.
"Mollywood" ita ce kawai tagwaye da ba ta buga bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma kuma ta guje wa bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, a ranar Jumma'a da yamma da kuma baya tara a ranar Jumma'a.
Wannan wasan, da kuma yadda makamashi ke gudana zuwa da daga masu kallo, ya tabbatar da cewa 'yan wasan ne za su ci a ranar Lahadi kuma babu wani dan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinari shahara don rufe wata nasara ta Turai yayin da rana ke faɗuwa a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau duka biyu a lokaci guda a ramuka daban-daban.
Ba a daɗe ba kafin a tattauna game da ɗaukakar Turai.
Baba Watson da Web Simpson sun saka wa Sergio Garcia, jarumin wasan kwallon kafa na safe, tabarau lokacin da yake wasa da Alex Noren.
Da bogey daya da biyu biyu a gaban tara sun jefa Spaniard da Sweden cikin rami mai zurfi ba za su iya fita ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga ramin.
Wasanni na hudu da na hudu suna da ban sha'awa sosai don kallon su a hankali saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, shawarwarin da ba su bayar ba, da kuma yadda dabarun zasu iya canzawa a cikin wani lokaci.
Turai ta fi kowa wasa a matsayin kungiya kuma tana da gagarumin ci gaba a rana ta karshe, amma wannan wasa na hudu ya kuma nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da karfin hali, duk da shakku da wasu ke da shi.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai za ta samu babban ci a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan da ta ci gaba a wasan hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar da ta doke Amurka da ci 10 da 6.
'Yan wasa biyu masu kwazo, Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun yi nasara a kan Tiger Woods, kuma sun ci gaba da zama a Le Golf National ta maki hudu.
Kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, wacce ke kokarin rike kambun da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta yi nasara a kan kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Amurka a wasan hudu da safe, inda ta ci 3-1.
Amurka ta fi tsayayya da su a cikin hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba za su iya rufe bambanci ba.
Jim Furik yana bukatar maki takwas daga cikin wasanni 12 da za a buga a ranar Lahadi domin ya ci gaba da cin kofin.
Fleetwood shine dan wasa na farko na Turai da ya fara cin kwallaye hudu a jere, yayin da tare da Molinari, wanda aka fi sani da "Mollywood", bayan wani karshen mako mai ban mamaki shine kawai biyu da suka samu maki hudu a cikin wasanni hudu na farko a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan hudu, sun hada karfi don murkushe Woods da kuma dan wasan Amurka Bryson Desapo tare da karin 5 & 4.
Woods, wanda ya yi fama da rashin lafiya a wasannin biyu da ya buga a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu fashewar haske, amma ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasansa 29 a wasan hudu da hudu da kuma wasanni bakwai.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta don wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ya koma abokin aikinsa Henryk Stenson don wasan kwallon kafa tare da 2 & 1 da Dustin Johnson da Brooks Kefka, suna cin nasara da farko da na uku a duniya.
Ba komai ya tafi daidai a Turai, duk da kyakkyawar rana mai sanyi a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spitth da Justin Thomas sun kafa wa Amurkawa maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara mai wuya 2&1 akan John Ram da Ian Poulter na Spain a cikin hudu kuma sun dawo daga baya don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a cikin foursome yayin da suka rasa ramuka biyu a buɗe.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da wata kungiya ta iya dawowa yayin da ta rasa ta da maki hudu a cikin singles, ko da yake saboda shi ne mai cin nasara, Furik ya isa ya ci nasara don riƙe da kyautar.
Amma bayan sun kasance a matsayi na biyu na kwana biyu, ya bayyana cewa sake kai hari a ranar Lahadi ba zai yiwu ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta yi watsi da makamai ba tare da amincewa ba.
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin da ake ci gaba da sanyawa na kara tsananta rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma kasarsa ba za ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyarta ba a karkashin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "manyan matakai na alheri" a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na ballistic, da kuma dakatar da cibiyoyin gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin hana yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba za a iya amincewa da tsaron kasa ba, kuma a karkashin irin wannan yanayi babu wata hanyar da za mu fara kawar da makamanmu".
Yayin da Ri ya sake maimaita sanannun korafin Koriya ta Arewa game da juriyar Washington game da yiwuwar "mataki-mataki" na nukiliya, wanda za a ba wa Koriya ta Arewa lada yayin da take ci gaba da aiwatar da aikin, sanarwar ta kasance mai mahimmanci saboda ba ta kawar da nukiliya ba, kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne game da sanarwar hadin gwiwar Kim Jong-un da Donald Trump a taron farko da aka yi tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don "rashin nukiliya na yankin Koriya", yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na neman kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara "bada" makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da kiran da ake yi na sassauta tsauraran takunkumin da aka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan cewa a fara yin nukiliya da farko kuma tana kara matsin lamba ta hanyar yin barazanar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar yin barazana, har ma da hana sanarwar kawo karshen yakin", in ji Ri.
"Ganin cewa takunkumi zai iya durƙusa mana mafarki ne ga waɗanda ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, tsauraran takunkumi na kara tsananta mana rashin amincewa".
Ri bai yi magana ba game da taron koli na biyu da aka shirya tsakanin Kim da Trump, wanda shugaban Amurka ya nuna a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Ministan, duk da haka, ya nuna tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: "Idan abokin tarayya a batun batun yaduwar nukiliya ya kasance Koriya ta Kudu maimakon Amurka, yaduwar yankin Koriya ba za ta kai ga irin wannan cikas ba".
Ko da yake, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bamban da na bara, lokacin da ya fadawa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin da ake kaiwa Amurka da makaman nukiliya na Koriya ta Arewa ba zai yiwu ba saboda "Mugun Shugaba" Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin makami mai linzami" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa a bara, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin zuciyarsa na ci gaba da matakan kwantar da hankali, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai sauran abubuwa da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da jadawalin wannan, yana cewa "Idan ya dauki shekaru biyu, ko uku ko watanni biyar, ba matsala".
China da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci ta ba Pyongyang lada kan matakin da ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Dole ne Majalisar Tsaro ta ci gaba da sanya takunkumi sosai kuma ba tare da tsayawa ba har sai an cimma cikakken, karshe da tabbatar da hana nukiliya".
Kwamitin tsaro ya amince da takunkumin da aka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa tun a shekarar 2006 a kokarin kawar da kudaden da take baiwa shirin nukiliyar da makamin kasar ta Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma tafiyarsa ta ƙarshe ba ta tafi da kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana cewa an samu ci gaba, sai Koriya ta Arewa ta tuhume shi sa'o'i kadan bayan haka da cewa yana da "bukatun wani dan daba".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a ganawar da ta yi da Moon a wannan watan cewa za ta rushe wani makamin nukiliya da kuma wani makami mai linzami idan Amurka ta dauki "matakan da suka dace".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake nema sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi wa Singapore kuma suna inganta daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna nazarin yadda za su samu isashen hutu
A wannan shekara, wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard ya bukaci dukan ɗaliban da ke karatun digiri na biyu su ƙara yin barci a ƙoƙarin magance al'adar yawan karatun dare da shan maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗalibai a babbar jami'a a duniya sau da yawa ba su san abubuwa na asali ba, kamar yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Chisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma likita ne a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya tsara wannan darasin, wanda ya yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a ƙasar Amirka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare ta ta fara darasin bayan wani jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
"A ƙarshe, wata yarinya ta zo ta ce, 'Me ya sa na soma koyo game da wannan a shekarata ta ƙarshe?'
Ta ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya mata game da muhimmancin barci - abin mamaki", in ji ta ga jaridar The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi, wanda aka fara a wannan shekarar, ya bayyana wa ɗalibai ƙa'idodin yadda yin barci da kyau zai taimaka wa ɗalibai su yi nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni, kuma su kasance da koshin lafiya.
Paul Barrera, farfesa a fannin ilimin hauka a makarantar kiwon lafiya ta Harvard da kuma shugaban jami'ar kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar haɗa darasin ne bayan da aka gano cewa ɗalibai suna rashin barci sosai a cikin mako.
Darasin sa'a ɗaya ya ƙunshi ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwanan dalibai, inda ɗalibai ke danna kofi, labule, takalman motsa jiki da littattafai don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki, da kuma mahimmancin tsarin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, masu halartar taron sun koyi cewa rashin barci na dogon lokaci yana iya sa mutum ya yi ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar, tare da gumaka masu ma'amala, suna ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da al'amuran yau da kullum.
"Mun san cewa ba zai canja halin ɗalibai nan da nan ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da hakkin su sani, kamar yadda kai ma kake da hakkin sanin sakamakon shan taba a kan lafiyarka", in ji Farfesa Chesler.
Al'adar yin fahariya don ka yi nazari duk dare ta ci gaba, in ji shi, ya daɗa cewa fasaha ta zamani da kuma matsi da ke ci gaba da ƙaruwa a kan ɗalibai yana nufin cewa rashin barci matsala ce mai girma.
Ya ce, samun isashen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama "makamin sirri" na ɗalibai don magance damuwa, gajiya, da kuma damuwa, har ma don guje wa yin kiba, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta yi yunwa, kuma hakan yana sa mutum ya ji yunwa sosai.
Raymond Shaw, ɗan shekara 19 daga California, wanda ke nazarin ilmin sunadarai da ilimin halittu, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Chisler wajen tsara darasin, ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin azuzuwansa a shekarar da ta shige, a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasin ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya sa ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba da darasi a ko'ina a makarantar.
Mataki na gaba, yana fatan, shine ya nemi dukkan daliban digiri su bi irin wannan shirin kafin su fara karatunsu a wannan makarantar da ke da matukar gasa.
Farfesa Chisler ya ce ɗalibai su kafa abin da zai gaya musu lokacin da za su yi barci da kuma ƙararrawa da za su yi amfani da ita don su san lokacin da za su farka, kuma su san cewa hasken da ke fitowa daga allon kwamfuta da kuma hasken LED zai iya ɓata tsarin motsin jiki kuma hakan zai iya sa su soma rashin barci.
Minga ta ci wa Gerard kwallo
Rangers sun sha wani mummunan rauni a waje, yayin da harbi na Dolly Minga ya jagoranci Steven Gerrard a cikin rashin daidaituwa a cikin 1-0 a Livingston.
Kungiyar Ibrox ta nemi nasarar farko a gida tun daga 4-1 da ta yi a St Johnstown a watan Fabrairu, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta jawo rashin nasara na biyu ga Gerrard a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, ta bar kungiyar ta maki takwas a bayan Harts, wanda ke kan gaba a gasar Ladbrokes.
Minga ya buga da minti bakwai kafin lokaci na farko kuma Rangers sun kasa ramawa.
Yayin da Rangers ta fadi zuwa ta shida, Livingston ta hau zuwa ta uku, da ci daya kawai daga Hibernian a gaba.
Kuma 'yan sanda na iya fuskantar wasu matsaloli, yayin da Sufeto Callum Spence ya bukaci taimakon gaggawa don rauni a kai wanda wani abu ya jefa daga filin wasa.
Gerard ya yi canje-canje takwas a cikin tawagar kuma ya ci Ayer a wasan kusa da na biyu na Betfred Cup.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya zo da wannan "Liv 11" wanda ya samu maki daga Harts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda wannan injin mai mai ya iya mamaye duk wani kokarin abokan hamayyarsa.
Rangers na iya zama masu rinjaye a kan tsaron, amma Livingston ta yi fiye da haka tare da kwallon.
Ya kamata ya ci a minti na biyu, lokacin da Minga ta fara wucewa ta tura Scott Pittman cikin yankin Alan McGregor, amma mai tsaron baya samun kwallon.
Kyakkyawan kyauta daga Keegan Jacobs ya sami shugaban Craig Halkett, amma abokin hamayyarsa Alan Lithgow ne kawai zai iya aikawa da ball daga cikin katako.
Rangers sun ci gaba da sarrafawa, amma akwai alamar akwai bege fiye da imani a wasan a ƙarshen kashi na uku.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi imanin cewa ya kamata ya ci kwallo a raga a minti na 15 yayin da ya yi karo da Steven Lawless, amma alkalin wasa Steven Thompson ya yi watsi da korafin ɗan Colombia.
Rangers sun samu ci biyu ne kawai a cikin rabin farko, amma tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ibrox, Liam Kelly, bai damu da ciwon kai na Lasana Coulibaly da kuma bugun da Ovi Edzariya ya yi ba.
Ko da yake a cikin minti 34 na farko na gasar Livy ta kasance ƙasa da tsammanin, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa ta cancanci nasara don ƙoƙari kawai.
Har yanzu Rangers sun kasa magance matsalar Jacobs.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba da kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya ci gaba da kasancewa da hankali kuma ya sami Minga wanda ya kammala ƙoƙarin.
Gerard ya sauya canjin a rabin lokaci ya fitar da Kullibali ya saka Ryan Kent, canjin ya biya kusan nan take, yayin da extreme ya ba da kwallon zuwa Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban mamaki ya tsere daga layinsa don toshe shi.
Duk da haka, Livingston ta ci gaba da jan hankalin baƙi zuwa ga wasan da ta sani da jin dadin, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna kawar da kwallon kafa daya bayan daya.
Holt ya iya karawa da bambanci a ƙarshen, amma McGregor ya fuskanci Jacobs a tsaye, ya dakatar da shi kafin ƙoƙarin Lithgow daga kusurwa.
A karshe, Glenn Middleton, wakilin Rangers, ya sake samun karin bugun daga hannun Jacobs, amma Thompson ya sake watsi da shi.
Almanac: Mai kirkirar Geiger counter
Shafi daga cikin littafin Sunday Morning: 30 ga Satumba, 1882: kamar yau, shekaru 136 da suka gabata kuma BAYA ... ranar da aka haifi mai zuwa a Jamus Johann Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanyar ganowa da kuma auna radiation. Wannan kirkire-kirkire ya haifar da na'urar da aka sani da Geiger counter.
A matsayin ginshiƙin kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger counter ya shiga cikin al'adun gargajiya, kamar fim ɗin 1950 mai suna Bells of Coronado, wanda ke nuna manyan masanan kimiyya Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan Geiger counter ne, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano abubuwa masu ɗauke da rediyo kamar uranium.
Idan ka sa waɗannan belun kunne, za ka ji motsin da ƙwayoyin halitta suke yi a ƙarfe".
Evans: "Duba, yana da hauka!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kaɗan kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Duk da haka, abin da ya samo asali ya ci gaba da aikinsa.
