Kit Harrington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin John Snow a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na HBO, Game of Thrones.
Amma, dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya soki yadda ake nuna shi a matsayin jarumi, yana cewa irin wannan rawar a kan allon tana ba wa yara maza cewa dole ne su kasance masu tsauri don samun girmamawa.
