HIV/Aids: Kasar Sin ta samu karin mutane 14 cikin 100 da suka kamu da cutar
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau.
A ƙasar, fiye da mutane 820,000 ne cutar ta shafa, in ji ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane 40,000.
A cikin mafi yawan lokuta, sabbin cututtukan suna yaduwa ta hanyar jima'i, suna nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar jinin da aka kamu da cutar.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya kusan ƙarewa, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na ƙasar Sin a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Amma idan aka gwada da shekarar da ta shige, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBTI a China.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi ya kasance ruwan dare gama gari.
Domin ɗabi'ar kasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke kwana da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka na wannan cuta suna faruwa ne saboda rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a kasar, a kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani jami'in ya fallasa bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican, ta la'anci "ƙarya mai haɗari" da "ka'idar maƙarƙashiya"
A ranar Asabar, wakilin majalisar wakilai na Amurka Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar wakilai uku a shafukan Wikipedia na majalisar.
'Yar majalisar wakilai ta Los Angeles ta ce masu sharhi da shafukan yanar gizo masu tsattsauran ra'ayi ne suka yi zargin.
"Maƙaryaci, ƙarya da ƙarin munanan ƙarya", Waters ta ce a cikin wata sanarwa a Twitter.
Bayanan da aka wallafa sun hada da adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanata Lindsey Graham na South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch na Utah.
Bayanai sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis kuma ya bayyana cewa wani mutum ne da ba a san shi ba daga yankin Capitol Hill ya wallafa shi a yayin sauraron kwamitin majalisar dattijai game da zargin cin zarafin mata a kan dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
An yi wannan bayanan ne bayan da 'yan majalisar uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya, kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState, sun ruwaito cewa adireshin IP da ke gano asalin abubuwan da aka sanya ya danganci ofishin Waters kuma sun buga bayanan wani ma'aikacin Waters, The Hill ya ruwaito.
"Wannan da'awar da ba ta da tushe ba ƙarya ce kwarai da gaske", in ji Waters.
