Fletcher ya yi kama da yadda Waters ta yi da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa Alkalin Kotun Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukarsa suka zargi da nuna fushi sosai a zaman kotun ranar Alhamis.
