Binciken fim din Johnny English ya sake bugawa - wani fim din leken asiri mai suna Rowan Atkinson
A yau al'ada ce mu nemi alamun Brexit a duk wani sabon fim da aka yi da ke nuna 'yan Birtaniya, kuma hakan na da kama da yadda ake yi a wannan fim din na fim din fim din da ke nuna jarumin Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 da Johnny English kuma ya dawo a 2011 da Johnny English: The Comeback.
Shin wannan baƙar magana ta ban dariya game da yadda muke da mummunan rauni zai zama sabuwar damar fitar da kayayyaki ta ƙasar?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny Inglis mai ƙarancin ƙarfi da ƙarancin ƙarfi ya sami damar sabunta lasisinsa don yin lalata a karo na biyu.
Wannan shi ne, ba shakka, mai aikin asiri wanda yake nuna cewa yana da haske da kuma hanyoyin da ake amfani da shi a matsayin wakili na sirri, yana kawo kadan ga Clouseau, tare da wani abu na "Mr. Bean" da kuma wani abu daga cikin mutumin da ya buga waƙa guda ɗaya a cikin fim din "Ways of Fire" a lokacin bikin bude gasar Olympics na London a shekarar 2012.
Hakanan ya dogara da matafiyi kuma baƙon ɗan adam na duniya wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin fim a cikin wasu shahararrun tallan talabijin na Barclaycard, yana haifar da rikici a hanyarsa.
Akwai wani abu mai kyau ko biyu a cikin wannan fim na JE.
Na ji daɗin lokacin da Johnny Inglis ya zo wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu sanye da kayan dāga kuma ya ji kamar an buga masa kwalkwali.
Atkinson yana nuna kwarewar sa a wasan kwaikwayo, duk da haka, wasan kwaikwayo yana da matukar damuwa da kuma ban mamaki, musamman ma lokacin da manyan fina-finai kamar 007 da Haɗari Mission sun hada da abubuwa masu ban dariya.
Abin dariya yana da kyau ga yara, ba manya ba, kuma a ganina, Johnny English ba shi da kwarewa da kuma dacewa kamar Atkinson ta silent movie sketches na mutumin Bean.
Babban batun da ke ci gaba da kasancewa shi ne cewa Birtaniya na da matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan leken asiri ya kutsa cikin wata babbar hanyar leken asiri ta yanar gizo ta Burtaniya, ya fallasa sunayen dukkan jami'an Burtaniya da ke aiki, abin takaici ga jami'in da ke aiki, wanda Kevin Elton ya buga a cikin wani karamin rawar da ya taka.
Ita ce ta ƙarshe ga wata firaminista mai son ci gaba da burin da ke kan iyakar lalacewa saboda rashin amincewar siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin mafi kyawun abin da za ta iya tare da wannan halin da ke tunatar da Theresa May, amma rubutun bai taimaka mata sosai ba.
Masu ba da shawara kan leken asiri sun sanar da ita cewa, tunda an gano duk wani ɗan leken asiri mai aiki, dole ne ta dawo da wani mara ƙarfi.
Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny Inglis, wanda yanzu yana aiki a matsayin darektan wata makarantar sakandare, amma yana koyar da darussan sirri: a nan akwai wasu kyawawan al'amuran yayin da Inglis ke ba da makarantar leken asiri irin ta One School Very Rock.
Inglis ya koma Whitehall don gaggawa na gaggawa kuma ya sake haɗuwa da tsohon abokin aikinsa Buff, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Yanzu Buff ya auri kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani aiki mai ban mamaki wanda Vicky Pepperdine ba ta amfani da shi sosai.
Don haka, Batman da Robin daga cikin ɓoye na Sirrin Sirrin Mai Girma sun dawo cikin aiki, suna haɗuwa da kyakkyawa da haɗari Ofelia Bulatova wanda Olga Kirilenko ke wasa.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista tana da matukar sha'awar wani mai kudi mai kudi mai kudi wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalar fasahar kasar: Jason Volta, mai tsoratar da mutane, wanda Jake Lacey ya buga.
Inglis da Buff sun fara odyssey na farce-comedy: suna yin kama da masu ba da abinci, suna cin wuta a wani gidan cin abinci na Faransa, suna haifar da rikici yayin da suke ƙoƙarin shiga cikin jirgin ruwa na Volta, kuma Inglis yana haifar da rashin adalci yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da na'urar gaskiya ta kama-da-wane don sanin cikin gidan Volta.
Dukkanin dabaru an yi amfani da su a wannan fim na ƙarshe, amma kamar yadda kyakkyawa da kuma m, har yanzu yana da ɗan gajeren talabijin na yara.
