Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana duba wani shiri na sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki na kwanaki hudu amma a biya su albashi na kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi nazari kan wani tsari na musamman da zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwanaki hudu a mako, amma a biya su albashi na kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce tana son shugabannin kamfanoni su ba ma'aikata karin ranar hutu daga aikin da suka samu daga fasahar kere kere.
Hakan zai ba ma'aikata damar yin hutu na kwana uku a mako ba tare da rage musu albashi ba.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayi ya yi daidai da tsarin tattalin arziki da kuma shirin jam'iyyar na karfafawa ma'aikata gwiwa.
An amince da sauya zuwa mako hudu a taron ma'aikata a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su amfana daga sauyin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban majiya a jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran za a sanar da sauyin manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
"Ba za a yi shi cikin dare ba, amma ranar aiki ta kwana hudu buri ne da ya yi daidai da tsarin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arzikin da ke goyon bayan ma'aikata da kuma tsarin jam'iyyar na masana'antu".
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da ta goyi bayan irin wannan ra'ayin ba, kamar yadda Jam'iyyar Green ta yi alkawarin mako hudu na aiki a yakin neman zaben shekara ta 2017.
Amma a halin yanzu, wannan ra'ayi ba shi da goyon baya daga duk 'yan jam'iyyar Labour.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Matsayin aiki na kwana hudu ba siyasa ba ce ta jam'iyyar kuma ba a tattauna ta da jam'iyyar ba".
Sakataren gwamnatin cikin gida, John McDonnell, ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour na makon da ya gabata don bayyana ra'ayinsa na juyin juya halin zamantakewar tattalin arziki.
McDonnell ya ce yana da niyyar dawo da iko daga "shugabanni marasa mutunci" da "masu son riba" a kamfanonin amfani.
Shirye-shiryen sakataren gwamnatin inuwa kuma na nufin cewa masu hannun jarin yanzu a kamfanonin ruwa ba za su iya dawo da duk hannun jarin su ba, saboda wata gwamnatin ma'aikata mai yuwuwa na iya yin "ƙuntatawa" saboda zargin rashin adalci.
Ya kuma tabbatar da tsare-tsaren sanya ma'aikata a kan kwamitocin kamfanoni da kuma samar da asusun haɗin gwiwa don ba da kashi 10% na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikata waɗanda za su sami ribar shekara-shekara har zuwa £ 500.
Lindsay Graham da John Kennedy sun tattauna a shirin 60 Minutes kan ko binciken FBI kan Kavanaugh zai iya sauya ra'ayinsu
Binciken da FBI ke yi kan zargin da ake yi wa Alkali Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta zabensa na zama babban alkalin kotun Amurka da akalla mako guda kuma ya tayar da tambaya kan ko binciken zai iya shafar wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da aka yi da shi a ranar Lahadi, Scott Pelley, wakilin shirin 60 Minutes, ya tambayi Sanata John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham na Republican ko FBI za ta iya gano duk wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya bayyana a fili fiye da abokin aikinsa daga South Carolina.
"Haka ne, ba shakka", in ji Kennedy.
"Na ce a kan hanyar zuwa kotu, na yi magana da Alkalin Kotun Kavano.
Na kira shi bayan wannan lokacin, lokacin da aka gabatar da rahoton, kuma na tambaye shi kai tsaye, "Me kuka yi?"
Ya kasance mai ƙwazo, mai ƙuduri, mai ƙuduri".
Duk da haka, ƙuri'ar Graham ba ta da wata ma'ana.
"Na yanke shawara game da Brett Kavanaugh kuma zai bukaci wani zargi mai tsanani don canza ra'ayina", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san wannan: Brett ya musanta hakan", in ji Graham, yana nufin Christine Blazy Ford.
"Kuma duk wanda ya ambata sunansa, ba zai iya tabbatar da hakan ba.
Shekaru 36 da suka shige.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu da zai canja".
Mene ne bikin Global Citizen Festival kuma ta yaya ya taimaka wajen rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara tare da babban shiri da fitattun taurari, amma kuma da manufa mai ban mamaki: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, dubun dubatar mutane ne za su yi tururuwa zuwa babban filin shakatawa na Central Park a matsayin wani ɓangare na bikin Global Citizen, ba wai kawai don jin daɗin masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron, wanda shine kawar da talauci ta 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan wadanda ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta zuwa taron (sai dai idan suna son siyan tikiti na VIP), masu sha'awar dole ne su kammala jerin ayyuka ko "ayyuka", kamar yin aikin sa kai, aika imel ga wani shugaban duniya, kira ko kuma wasu hanyoyi masu mahimmanci don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar Global Citizen take, yayin da muke da sauran shekaru 12 kafin cimma burinmu?
Shin ra'ayin lada tare da kyauta kyauta shine hanya madaidaiciya don shawo kan 'yan uwanmu suyi aiki ko kuma kawai wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "click activism", wanda shine lokacin da wasu ke jin cewa suna da gaske yin canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takardar neman izini ta hanyar imel ko aika tweet?
Tun daga 2011, kungiyar Global Citizen ta ce ta samu sama da "aiki" miliyan 19 daga magoya bayanta, suna tallata wasu manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce waɗannan ayyuka sun taimaka wa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37, waɗanda za su shafi rayukan mutane fiye da biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta ba da rahoton alkawura da sanarwa 390 sakamakon waɗannan ayyukan, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka kashe ko aka tara.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka bayar sun shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiyar masu saka jari da masu aiwatarwa a Burtaniya, wadanda suka dauki alkawarin "taimaka wa yara su cika damar su", ta hanyar yin alkawarin ba Rwanda dala miliyan 35 don kawar da karancin abinci mai gina jiki, bayan da suka karbi tweets sama da 4,700 daga 'yan kungiyar Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin kasa da membobin al'ummar Global Citizens kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a cikin tarihi", in ji Tracy Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, ga masu sauraro yayin wasan kwaikwayon a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce, bayan da aka dauki matakai sama da 5,000 da suka bukaci Birtaniya ta inganta abinci ga mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da bada tallafi ga wani shiri mai suna The Power of Nutrition, wanda ya shafi mata da yara miliyan 5 da ke fama da matsalar abinci.
A cikin amsar tambayar "Me ya sa kake tsammanin za mu iya kawar da talauci?"
wani memba na al'ummar Global Citizen ya amsa: "Hanyar za ta yi tsawo kuma mai wuya, a wasu lokatai za mu faɗi kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar dukkan manyan ƙungiyoyin kare haƙƙin ɗan adam da na anti-apartheid da suka gabace mu, za mu yi nasara, domin idan muka kasance tare za mu fi ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, Wicket, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B da Janelle Mona wasu daga cikin masu zane-zane ne da za su fito a bikin a New York na wannan shekara, wanda Deborah-Lee Farnes da Hugh Jackman za su gabatar.
Amurka na iya amfani da sojan ruwanta wajen hana Rasha fitar da makamashi -Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida
Washington na iya amfani da sojojinta na ruwa "idan ya cancanta" don hana samar da makamashin Rasha a kasuwannin ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, kamar yadda Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke ya bayyana, a cewar Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Syria, inda take aiki a gayyatar da gwamnatin da ta dace, wata hujja ce ta bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shine suna son sayar da makamashi, kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin da kudancin Turai", in ji shi a cewar rahotanni.
A cewar ministan, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin da za a magance ayyukan Rasha.
"Amurka tana da damar, tare da goyon bayan sojin ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa za su kasance a bude kuma, idan ya cancanta, toshe su, don tabbatar da cewa ba za a iya sayar da makamashin Rasha ba", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ne a wani taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke bayyana kanta a matsayin "muryar mai amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya yi karin haske kan yadda Amurka ke tunkarar Rasha da Iran, inda ya ce sun yi kama da juna.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha shine, da yawa, amfani da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yana mai kiran Rasha "farar fata da ta san dabara ɗaya kawai", saboda tana da tattalin arzikin da ke dogara da burbushin mai.
Bayanan sun zo ne yayin da gwamnatin Trump ta dauki nauyin bunkasa fitar da iskar gas ta Amurka zuwa Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ita ce mafi arha ga masu amfani da ita a Turai.
Saboda haka, gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da Shugaba Donald Trump kansa, na kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin da ba daidai ba na Nord Stream 2 wanda, a cewar Trump, zai sa Berlin ta zama "ciki" na Moscow.
Moscow ta sha jaddada cewa bututun Nord Stream 2, wanda aka tsara a kan dala biliyan 11, wanda zai ninka karfin bututun zuwa mita biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya yi ikirarin cewa Washington ta yi tsayayya da aikin ne saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na gasa mara kyau.
"Ina ganin mun yarda cewa ba za a iya amfani da makamashi a matsayin hanyar matsa lamba ba kuma masu amfani da su su sami damar zaɓar mai samar da iskar gas da suke so", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Alexander Novak bayan ganawa da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Wannan matakin na Amurka ya jawo martani daga Jamus, wadda ta jaddada jajircewarta wajen aiwatar da aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta janye daga manufofin samar da makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar kasashen biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kemph, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawarsa da Angela Merkel da Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben.
A wani taron da aka yi a ofishin shugabancin garin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa tana duba batun.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ke cikin matsala, kuma hakan na bukatar mace a kan kujerar", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da yiwuwar neman shugaban kasa".
Warren ta soki Shugaba Donald Trump a yayin taron, tana cewa "yana jagorantar kasar cikin hanyar da ba daidai ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji shi.
Warren ta yi magana da yawa game da Trump da kuma ɗan takarar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
A wani tweet a ranar Juma'a, Warren ta ce "ba shakka akwai bukatar binciken FBI kafin zaben".
Wani binciken da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis, duk da haka, ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'ar Warren ba su yi imani da cewa ya kamata ya nemi shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020 ba.
Kashi 58% na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata 'yar majalisar ba ta tsayawa takara, a cewar wani binciken da Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe ta yi.
