Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan batun sabon tsarin neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan batun batun sabuwar manufar Amurka da ke hana ba da mafaka ga wadanda ke kokarin tserewa daga 'yan bindiga ko tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da gundumar sun gabatar da rahoton amicus curiae a ranar Juma'a a Washington don tallafawa wani mai neman mafaka don kalubalanci manufar, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace da Sessions da Civil Liberties Union ta shigar a watan Agusta ba game da manufar tarayya.
Ta ce mijinta "da 'ya'yansa maza masu cin zarafi da ke cikin ƙungiya" suna cin zarafinta, amma jami'an Amurka sun ƙi ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare shi a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, inda yawancin masu neman mafaka a Amurka suka fito, a matsayin kasashen da ke fama da matsalolin 'yan bindiga da tashin hankali a cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta sauya shawarar da Kwamitin Kula da Shige da Fice (BIA) ya yanke a 2014 kuma ya ba da damar baƙi da ba a bayyana ba waɗanda ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida su nemi mafaka.
Babban lauyan yankin Columbia, Karl Racine, ya ce a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na jihohi, tarayya da kuma dokokin duniya".
"Dangane da dokar tarayya, dole ne a bincika duk buƙatun mafaka bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da yanayin aikace-aikacen. Irin wannan ƙuntatawa ya karya wannan ƙa'idar", in ji rahoton amicus curiae.
Lauyoyin sun kuma yi ikirarin cewa, wannan manufofin na hana masu shigowa kasar na cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna mai cewa, 'yan kasashen waje sun fi zama 'yan kasuwa kuma suna da matukar muhimmanci a cikin ma'aikata.
A watan Yuni, Babban Lauyan Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shari'ar shige da fice da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke ƙoƙarin tserewa daga tashin hankali da ƙungiyoyin 'yan bindiga.
"Sai dai, an bai wa 'yan gudun hijira damar barin kasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko barazana saboda launin fata, addini, kasa ko kuma kasancewa cikin wata kungiya ko siyasa", in ji Sessions a cikin sanarwar da ya fitar a ranar 11 ga watan Yuni.
Manufar mafaka ba ta taɓa zama ta rage dukan matsaloli (har ma da mafi tsanani) da mutane ke fuskanta a kowace rana a dukan duniya ba.
