Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar majiyoyin gwamnati, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Da yake an katse sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su samu damar samun bayanai daga Dongala ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palo, wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palau, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in ya barke.
