Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya ne, wanda ke gefen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan mazauna 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Dongala wata masarauta ce da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) a gabar teku a kudu maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, wani matakin rarrabuwa na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardin, yana da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan abubuwan da ke tallafawa tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Harkokin hakar ma'adinai na Nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an fi samunsa a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Masu ba da agajin bala'i a Indonesia sun ce, tsunamis ya addabi Palu da Dongala sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige.
A shekara ta 1938, wata guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Dongala.
Tsunami kuma ya afkawa yammacin Tonga a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
