Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya auku a gabar teku ta kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 a kan ma'aunin Richter da ke kusa da garin Pandang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Medawi, kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
