Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi a yankewa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci hukuncin kisa a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun nemi a yankewa Saifullo Saifov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba saboda aikata laifi a tarayya tun 1953.
Saifov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan West Side Avenue a Lower Manhattan, yana jan ƙafafun da masu hawan keke da suka shiga hanyarsa a ranar 31 ga Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipoff ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni da gangan, a cewar sanarwar niyyar yanke hukuncin kisa da aka shigar a Kotun Kudancin New York.
Dukkanin waɗannan laifuka suna da hukuncin kisa, a cewar rubutun.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta gabatar da Saipov a kan tuhumar da ta kunshi abubuwa 22, wadanda suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai da ake yi wa kungiyar 'yan ta'adda, wata dabara da ake amfani da ita a lokuta da dama a shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma laifuka daya na aikata tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci "babban shiri da tunani", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna mai bayyana yadda Saipoff ya kai harin a matsayin "abin ƙyama, mugunta da lalata".
"Saifullo Habibullayevich Saipoff ya haifar da wahala, lahani da asarar rayuka ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Anhelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Ann-Lore Decad, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlich, Ernan Ferruzzi, Ernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Panuko", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shude tun lokacin da Kotun Southern District na New York ta yi shari'a a kan batun da ke neman hukuncin kisa.
