A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa a New York a kan wani shari'a da aka yi a tarayya. An kashe ma'aurata Julius da Ethel Rosenberg bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg biyu a kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
